            <title>[LANG-969] StringUtils.toEncodedString(byte[], Charset) needlessly throws UnsupportedEncodingException</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/LANG-969</link>
                <project id="12310481" key="LANG">Commons Lang</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;This new method throws UnsupportedEncodingException when passed in a Charset object. Why?&lt;/p&gt;

